description: Lizhi, Inc. owns and operates an interactive audio entertainment platform and an online audio platform in China. The company's app Lizhi allows users to create, store and share their own podcasts on mobile devices with the help of intuitive recording and reach their audience through various discovery tools. Lizhi was founded by Jinnan Lai and Ning Ding in November 2010 and is headquartered in Guangzhou, China.
